caption.p: ( a) Initial discharge/charge curves of B-SFO@C, B-SO@C and B-SFO electrodes at 0.2 A g −1 in the potential range of 0.005–3.0 V, ( b) cyclic behavior at 0.2 A g −1 and ( c) rate capability summary at various current densities from 0.2 A g −1 to 3.2 A g −1 of three electrodes, long-term high-rate cycling performance of the B-SFO@C electrode at ( d) 1 A g −1 and ( e) 3 A g −1.
